default6.1.10.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAn additional cost for CTOs is for safety equipment suc
defaulth as wheelchair restraints (front and back), wheel chair occupant safety seat belt re
defaultstraints, seat belt extensions.  The cost is on average £600 per wheelchair.  Some CTOs have up to £3,000 of additional safety equipment on each bus.
